OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMost places having a fine and
OL,6,Fdry day, with plenty of warm spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine. However, it will generally
OL,8,Fbe cloudier across Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fand western Scotland, with an
OL,10,Fincreasing risk of showery rain here.
OL,11,FWinds lighter than on Thursday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fwill continue across parts of Scotland
OL,15,Fand Northern Ireland, pushing into
OL,16,Fwestern parts of England and Wales.
OL,17,FClear spells holding on across
OL,18,Fsoutheast England. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
