OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy in the north
OL,6,Fand west, with some patchy rain. This
OL,7,Fbecoming mainly confined to western
OL,8,FScotland by the evening. Warm spells
OL,9,Fof sunshine developing across much of
OL,10,FEngland.
